    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>rump steak</strong> over the <strong>creamy mustard sauce</strong> with the <strong>Parmentier potatoes</strong> and <strong>garlicky green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
